main event: A UFO sighting involving four unidentified objects was reported at a munitions plant in Neosho, Missouri on October 29, 1962.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 2 minutes,The objects were observed using ground radar,The course of the objects was described as erratic,Details of the sightings were confirmed by Bolio/AFS authorities,The objects were identified as rectangular and green.
witness description: Details are not provided regarding witnesses.
